	<p class=" font-outfit font-semibold text-darkblue-500 text-xl ">Som din digitale forretningspartner er du derfor garanteret ren snak for pengene, og at vi holder vores aftaler, og indfrier de løfter, vi giver.</p>
	<div class="grid place-content-center md:place-content-start"><Button variant="secondary" >Lær os at kende</Button></div> 
	</div>
	<Image src={besa} alt="" class="w-full order-first md:order-last"/>
</section>

		</article>

			<!-------------------------------- OM BESA SEKTION SLUT ---------------------->





			<!-------------------------------- SERVICES SEKTION  ---------------------->

	<section id="service" class="px-6 md:px-24 mb-32 md:mb-56">
